#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Entries"
msgstr "Vnosi v meniju"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>starts a new document</action> in the editing window. "
"In the <guibutton>Documents</guibutton> list on the left the new file is "
"named <emphasis>Untitled</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz <action>začne nov dokument</action> v oknu za urejanje. Na seznamu "
"<guibutton>Dokumenti</guibutton> na levi je nova datoteka poimenovana "
"<emphasis>Brez naslova</emphasis>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a standard &kde; <guilabel>Open File</guilabel> dialog. Use the "
"file view to select the file you want to open, and click on <guibutton>Open</"
"guibutton> to open it."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže standardni &kde; Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Odpri datoteko</guilabel>. "
"Uporabite pogled datoteke, da izberete datoteko, ki jo želite odpreti, in "
"kliknite <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>, da jo odprete."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open Recent</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri nedavno</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a shortcut to open recently saved documents. Clicking on this item "
"opens a list to the side of the menu with several of the most recently saved "
"files. Clicking on a specific file will open it in &kappname; - if the file "
"still resides at the same location."
msgstr ""
"To je bližnjica za odpiranje nedavno shranjenih dokumentov. S klikom na ta "
"element se ob strani menija odpre seznam z več nazadnje shranjenimi "
"datotekami. S klikom na določeno datoteko se ta odpre v &kappname; - če je "
"datoteka še vedno na istem mestu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Open With</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri z</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu presents a list of applications known to handle the &MIME; type "
"of your current document. Activating an entry will open the current document "
"with that application."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni predstavlja seznam aplikacij, za katere je znano, da obravnavajo "
"&MIME; vrsto vašega trenutnega dokumenta. Z aktiviranjem vnosa se odpre "
"trenutni dokument s to aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, an entry <guimenuitem>Other...</guimenuitem> launches the open "
"with dialog box that allows you to <action>select another application to "
"open the active file</action>. Your file will still be open in &kate;."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega vnos <guimenuitem>Drugo ...</guimenuitem> zažene pogovorno okno "
"Odpri z, ki vam omogoča, da <action>izberete drugo aplikacijo za odpiranje "
"aktivne datoteke</action>. Vaša datoteka bo še vedno odprta v &kate;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This saves the current document. If there has already been a save of the "
"document then this will overwrite the previously saved file without asking "
"for the user's consent. If it is the first save of a new document the save "
"as dialog (described below) will be invoked."
msgstr ""
"To shrani trenutni dokument. Če je dokument že bil shranjen, bo to prepisalo "
"predhodno shranjeno datoteko, ne da bi uporabnik vprašal za soglasje. Če gre "
"za prvo shranjevanje novega dokumenta, se odpre pogovorno okno za "
"shranjevanje kot (opisano spodaj)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot ..."
"</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows a document to be saved with a new file name. This is done by "
"means of the file dialog box described above in the <link linkend=\"file-open"
"\">Open</link> section of this help file."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča shranjevanje dokumenta z novim imenom datoteke. To storite s "
"pomočjo pogovornega okna datoteke, opisanega zgoraj v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"file-open\">Odpri</link> te datoteke pomoči."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As with Encoding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot s kodiranjem</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save a document with a new file name in a different encoding."
msgstr "Shranite dokument z novim imenom datoteke v drugem kodiranju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Copy As</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kopijo kot</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save a copy of the document with a new file name and continue editing the "
"original document."
msgstr ""
"Shranite kopijo dokumenta z novim imenom datoteke in nadaljujte z urejanjem "
"izvirnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command <action>saves all modified open files</action>."
msgstr "Ta ukaz <action>shrani vse spremenjene odprte datoteke</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reloads the active file from disk. This command is useful if another program "
"or process has changed the file while you have it open in &kappname;."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži aktivno datoteko z diska. Ta ukaz je uporaben, če je drug "
"program ali proces spremenil datoteko, medtem ko jo imate odprto v "
"&kappname;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Znova naloži vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Reloads all opened files.</action>."
msgstr "<action>Znova naloži vse odprte datoteke.</action>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a simple print dialog allowing the user to specify what, where, and "
"how to print."
msgstr ""
"Odpre preprosto pogovorno okno za tiskanje, ki uporabniku omogoča, da "
"določi, kaj, kje in kako naj tiska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export as HTML</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi kot HTML</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the currently open document as an &HTML; file, which will be formatted "
"using the current syntax highlighting and color scheme settings."
msgstr ""
"Shranite trenutno odprt dokument kot &HTML; datoteka, ki bo oblikovana s "
"trenutnim označevanjem sintakse in nastavitvami barvne sheme."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the active file with this command. If you have made unsaved changes, "
"you will be prompted to save the file before &kate; closes it."
msgstr ""
"S tem ukazom zaprite aktivno datoteko. Če ste naredili neshranjene "
"spremembe, boste pozvani, da shranite datoteko, preden &kate; ga zapre."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Other</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri drugo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close other open documents."
msgstr "Zapri druge odprte dokumente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>closes all the files you have open</action> in &kate;."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz <action>zapre vse datoteke, ki ste jih odprli</action> v &kate;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Orphaned</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri osirotel</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Close</action> all documents in the file list, which could not be "
"reopened during startup, because they are not accessible anymore."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zapri</action> vse dokumente na seznamu datotek, ki jih med zagonom "
"ni bilo mogoče znova odpreti, ker niso več dostopni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command <action>closes &kate;</action> and any files you were editing. "
"If you have made unsaved changes to any of the files you were editing, you "
"will be prompted to save them."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz <action>zapre &kate;</action> in vse datoteke, ki ste jih urejali. "
"Če ste naredili neshranjene spremembe katere koli od datotek, ki ste jih "
"urejali, boste pozvani, da jih shranite."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last editing command (typing, copying, cutting &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Razveljavi zadnji ukaz za urejanje (tipkanje, kopiranje, rezanje &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may undo several editing commands of the same type, like typing in "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"To lahko razveljavi več ukazov za urejanje iste vrste, na primer vnašanje "
"znakov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will reverse the most recent change (if any) made using Undo."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste razveljavili najnovejšo spremembo (če obstaja), narejeno s "
"funkcijo Razveljavi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the current selection and places it on the clipboard. "
"The clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to transfer data between "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz izbriše trenutni izbor in ga postavi v odložišče. Odložišče deluje "
"nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This copies the currently selected text to the clipboard so that it may be "
"pasted elsewhere. The clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to "
"transfer data between applications."
msgstr ""
"S tem kopirate trenutno izbrano besedilo v odložišče, da ga lahko prilepite "
"drugam. Odložišče deluje nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will insert the first item in the clipboard at the cursor position. The "
"clipboard works invisibly and provides a way to transfer data between "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"To bo vstavilo prvi element v odložišče na položaj kazalke. Odložišče deluje "
"nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Overwrite Selection is enabled, the pasted text will overwrite the "
"selection, if any."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost Prepiši izbor, bo prilepljeno besedilo prepisalo "
"izbor, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Ins;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Ins;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi izbor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will paste the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">mouse selection</ulink> contents "
"that were chosen previously. Mark some text with the mouse pointer to paste "
"it in the currently open file using this menu item."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste prilepili vsebino <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">izbire miške</ulink>, ki je bila "
"predhodno izbrana. Označite nekaj besedila s kazalcem miške, da ga prilepite "
"v trenutno odprto datoteko s tem elementom menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Swap with clipboard contents</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zamenjaj z vsebino odložišča</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will swap the selected text with the <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">clipboard</ulink> contents."
msgstr ""
"To bo zamenjalo izbrano besedilo z vsebino <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Clipboard_(computing)#X_Window_System\">odložišča</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Clipboard History</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zgodovina odložišča</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu will display the beginning of portions of text recently copied "
"to the clipboard. Select an item from this menu to paste it in the currently "
"open file."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni bo prikazal začetek delov besedila, ki so bili nedavno kopirani v "
"odložišče. V tem meniju izberite element, da ga prilepite v trenutno odprto "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy as HTML</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj kot HTML</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy the selection as &HTML;, formatted using the current syntax "
"highlighting and color scheme settings."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte izbor kot &HTML;, oblikovan z uporabo trenutnega označevanja "
"sintakse in nastavitev barvne sheme."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will select the entire document. This could be very useful for copying "
"the entire file to another application."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste izbrali celoten dokument. To je lahko zelo koristno za kopiranje "
"celotne datoteke v drugo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prekliči izbiro</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deselects the selected text in the editor if any."
msgstr "Prekliče izbiro izbranega besedila v urejevalniku, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Block Selection "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Blokiraj način "
"izbire</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles Selection Mode. When the Selection Mode is <guilabel>BLOCK</"
"guilabel>, the status bar contains the string <guilabel>[BLOCK]</guilabel> "
"and you can make vertical selections, &eg; select column 5 to 10 in lines 9 "
"to 15."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi način izbire. Ko je izbirni način <guilabel>BLOKIRAJ</guilabel>, "
"statusna vrstica vsebuje niz <guilabel>[BLOKIRAJ]</guilabel> in lahko "
"izbirate navpično, &eg; izberite stolpec od 5 do 10 v vrsticah od 9 do 15."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Input Modes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Načini vnosa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch between a normal and a vi-like, modal editing mode. The vi input mode "
"supports the most used commands and motions from vim's normal and visual "
"mode and has an optional vi mode statusbar. This status bar shows commands "
"while they are being entered, output from commands and the current mode. The "
"behavior of this mode can be configured in the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"config-dialog-editor.html#pref-edit-vi-input-mode\">Vi Input Mode</ulink> "
"section of the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page in &kappname;'s settings "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljajte med običajnim in modalnim načinom urejanja, podobnim vi. Način "
"vnosa vi podpira najpogosteje uporabljene ukaze in gibe iz normalnega in "
"vizualnega načina vim in ima izbirno statusno vrstico načina vi. Ta statusna "
"vrstica prikazuje ukaze med vnašanjem, izhod iz ukazov in trenutni način. "
"Delovanje tega načina je mogoče konfigurirati v razdelku <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#pref-edit-vi-input-mode\">Način vnosa Vi</"
"ulink> v stran <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami &kappname;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ins</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Overwrite Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ins</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način prepisovanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the Insert/Overwrite modes. When the mode is <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, you insert characters where the cursor is. When the mode is "
"<guilabel>OVR</guilabel>, writing characters will replace the current "
"characters if your cursor is positioned before any character. The status bar "
"shows the current state of the Overwrite Mode, either <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>OVR</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi med načini Vstavljanje/Prepisovanje. Ko je način <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, vstavite znake tam, kjer je kazalec. Ko je način <guilabel>OVR</"
"guilabel>, bodo pisni znaki zamenjali trenutne znake, če je vaš kazalec "
"postavljen pred kateri koli znak. Statusna vrstica prikazuje trenutno stanje "
"načina prepisovanja, <guilabel>INS</guilabel> ali <guilabel>OVR</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the incremental search bar at the bottom of the editor window. On "
"the left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed "
"by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za postopno iskanje na dnu okna urejevalnika. Na levi "
"strani vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno "
"besedilno polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start entering characters of your search pattern, the search starts "
"immediately. If there is a match in the text this is highlighted and the "
"background color of the entry field changes to light green. If the search "
"pattern does not match any string in the text, this is indicated by a light "
"red background color of the entry field."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete vnašati znake svojega iskalnega vzorca, se iskanje začne takoj. "
"Če se besedilo ujema, je to označeno in barva ozadja vnosnega polja se "
"spremeni v svetlo zeleno. Če se iskalni vzorec ne ujema z nobenim nizom v "
"besedilu, je to označeno s svetlo rdečo barvo ozadja vnosnega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:505 menus.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> or "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to jump to the "
"next or previous match in the document."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> gumb za skok na "
"naslednje ali prejšnje ujemanje v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches in the document are highlighted even when you close the search bar. "
"To clear this highlighting, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr ""
"Ujemanja v dokumentu so označena tudi, ko zaprete iskalno vrstico. Če želite "
"počistiti to označevanje, pritisnite &Esc; ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the search should be case sensitive. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali naj iskanje razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. Če "
"izberete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili najdbe na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the incremental search bar to switch to the power "
"search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Klikni na <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> gumb "
"na desni strani iskalne vrstice Za preklop na vrstica za iskanje in "
"zamenjavo moči."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Poišči naslednje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar, and searching forwards through the document starting "
"from the cursor position."
msgstr ""
"To ponovi zadnjo operacijo iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica prirastne iskalne "
"vrstice in iskanja naprej po dokumentu, začenši od položaja kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar, and searching backwards instead of forwards through "
"the document."
msgstr ""
"S tem se ponovi zadnja operacija iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica prirastne "
"iskalne vrstice in iskanja nazaj namesto naprej po dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find Selected</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Poišči Izbrano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds next occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče naslednjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Variants</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Find Selected Backwards</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči različice</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Poišči izbrano za nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds previous occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče prejšnjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Replace...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zamenjaj ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command opens the power search and replace bar. On the upper left side "
"of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed by a small "
"text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz odpre vrstico za iskanje in zamenjavo. Na zgornji levi strani "
"vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno besedilno "
"polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the search mode by selecting <guilabel>Plain text</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Whole words</guilabel>, <guilabel>Escape sequences</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</guilabel> from the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Način iskanja lahko nadzirate tako, da na padajočem meniju izberete "
"<guilabel>Navadno besedilo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Cele besede</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni izraz</"
"guilabel> navzdol škatla."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Escape sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</"
"guilabel> are selected, the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> menuitem at the "
"bottom of the context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you "
"to add escape sequences or regular expression items to the search or replace "
"pattern from predefined lists."
msgstr ""
"Če so izbrana <guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni "
"izraz</guilabel>, bo omogočen menijski element <guibutton>Dodaj ...</"
"guibutton> na dnu priročnega menija besedilnih polj in vam omogoča dodajanje "
"ubežnih zaporedij ali postavk regularnega izraza v vzorec iskanja ali "
"zamenjave iz vnaprej določenih seznamov."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the text to replace with in the text box labeled <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> and click the <guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace "
"only the highlighted text or the <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> button "
"to replace the search text in the whole document."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje z oznako <guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel> vnesite besedilo, s "
"katerim želite zamenjati, in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, "
"da zamenjate samo označeno besedilo, ali gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj vse</"
"guibutton>, da zamenjajte iskalno besedilo v celotnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the search and replace behavior by selecting different "
"options at the bottom of the bar. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern. <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> will search and replace within the current selection "
"only. The <guilabel>Find All</guilabel> button highlights all matches in the "
"document and shows the number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Obnašanje iskanja in zamenjave lahko spremenite tako, da izberete različne "
"možnosti na dnu vrstice. Če izberete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili iskanje na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu. "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> bo iskal in zamenjal "
"samo znotraj trenutnega izbora. Gumb <guilabel>Najdi vse</guilabel> označi "
"vse zadetke v dokumentu in prikaže število najdenih zadetkov v majhnem "
"pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the power search and replace bar to switch to the "
"incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> na "
"desni strani zmogljive vrstice za iskanje in zamenjavo za preklopite na "
"vrstico za postopno iskanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go To</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Go to Matching Bracket</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pojdi v ujemajoči oklepaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the cursor to the associated opening or closing bracket."
msgstr "Kazalec premaknite na ustrezni začetni ali zaključni oklepaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go To</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Select to Matching Bracket</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Izberi ujemajoči se oklepaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the text between associated opening and closing brackets."
msgstr "Izbere besedilo med povezanimi začetnimi in končnimi oklepaji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go To</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Go to "
"Previous Modified Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pojdi na prejšnjo spremenjeno vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that were changed since opening the file are called modified lines. "
"This action jumps the previous modified line."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki so bile spremenjene od odprtja datoteke, se imenujejo "
"spremenjene vrstice. To dejanje preskoči prejšnjo spremenjeno vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go To</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Go to "
"Next Modified Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pojdi na naslednjo spremenjeno vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that were changed since opening the file are called modified lines. "
"This action jumps the next modified line."
msgstr ""
"Vrstice, ki so bile spremenjene od odprtja datoteke, se imenujejo "
"spremenjene vrstice. To dejanje preskoči naslednjo spremenjeno vrstico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go To</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Go to Line...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pojdi v vrstico...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the goto line bar at the bottom of the window which is used to "
"have the cursor jump to a particular line (specified by number) in the "
"document. The line number may be entered directly into the text box or "
"graphically by clicking on the up or down arrow spin controls at the side of "
"the text box. The little up arrow will increase the line number and the down "
"arrow decrease it. Close the bar with a click on the button with an icon on "
"the left side of the bar."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za prehod na vrstico na dnu okna, ki se uporablja za skok "
"kazalca na določeno vrstico (določeno s številko) v dokumentu. Številko "
"vrstice lahko vnesete neposredno v besedilno polje ali grafično s klikom na "
"puščico gor ali dol ob strani besedilnega polja. Majhna puščica navzgor "
"poveča številko vrstice, puščica navzdol pa zmanjša. Vrstico zapremo s "
"klikom na gumb z ikono na levi strani vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens another instance of &kate;</action>. The new instance will be "
"identical to your previous instance."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre drug primerek &kate;</action>. Nov primerek bo enak vašemu "
"prejšnjemu primerku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednji zavihek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activates the next tab in the tabbar."
msgstr "Aktivira naslednji zavihek v vrstici z zavihki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji zavihek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activates the previous tab in the tabbar."
msgstr "Aktivira prejšnji zavihek v vrstici z zavihki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reopen Latest "
"Closed Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Poglej</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovno odpri "
"zadnji zaprti dokument</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reopens the latest closed document or documents."
msgstr "Ponovno odpri zadnje zaprti dokument ali dokumente."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quick Open</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hitro "
"odpiranje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show a search field and a list of opened files in the editor area. While "
"entering text in the search field the document names and document &URL;s are "
"searched for matching text. While entering text in the search field you can "
"use the cursor keys &Up; and &Down; to navigate in the list view. Pressing "
"the &Enter; key or double clicking on an item in the list switches the view "
"to the document selected in the list view. This makes switching between "
"documents easier, if there are a lot of them open."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži iskalno polje in seznam odprtih datotek v območju urejevalnika. Med "
"vnašanjem besedila v iskalno polje se iščejo imena dokumentov in URL-ji "
"dokumentov za ujemajoče se besedilo. Med vnosom besedila v iskalno polje "
"lahko uporabite smerne tipke &Up; in &Down; za krmarjenje v pogledu seznama. "
"S pritiskom tipke &Enter; tipko ali dvojni klik na element na seznamu "
"preklopi pogled na dokument, izbran v pogledu seznama. To olajša "
"preklapljanje med dokumenti, če jih je veliko odprtih."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action is available also using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon at the top right of "
"the editor window."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje je na voljo tudi z uporabo ikone "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> v zgornjem desnem kotu "
"okna urejevalnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F8</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Previous Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F8</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji Razdeljen pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the previous document view, if you have split the editor area in more "
"views."
msgstr ""
"Osredotočite pogled prejšnjega dokumenta, če ste razdelili območje "
"urejevalnika na več pogledov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Next Split View</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F8</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednji razdeljeni "
"pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the next document view, if you have split the editor area in more "
"views."
msgstr ""
"Osredotočite se na naslednji pogled dokumenta, če ste območje urejevalnika "
"razdelili na več pogledov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Left Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Levi deljeni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively on the left, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Intuitivno osredotočite razdeljeni pogled na levo in po potrebi uporabite "
"položaj kazalca za razjasnitev dvoumnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Right Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Desni deljeni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively on the right, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Intuitivno osredotočite razdeljeni pogled na desno, po potrebi uporabite "
"položaj kazalca za razjasnitev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Upward Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Deljeni pogled navzgor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively upward, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Izostrite razdeljeni pogled intuitivno navzgor z uporabo položaja kazalca za "
"razjasnitev, če je potrebno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Downward Split View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Deljen pogled navzdol</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the split view intuitively downward, using the cursor position to "
"disambiguate if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Izostrite razdeljeni pogled intuitivno navzdol, po potrebi uporabite položaj "
"kazalca za razjasnitev dvoumnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Split Vertical</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Razdeli navpično</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the frame (which may be the main editing area) in two "
"equally sized frames, the new one to the left of the current one. The new "
"frame gets the focus, and will display the same document as the old one."
msgstr ""
"To bo razdelilo okvir (ki je lahko glavno območje za urejanje) na dva "
"okvirja enake velikosti, novega bo levo od trenutnega. Novi okvir dobi fokus "
"in bo prikazal isti dokument kot stari."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:873 menus.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid "See also <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Working with the &kate; MDI</link>."
msgstr "Glejte tudi <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Delo z &kate; MDI</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Split Horizontal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Razdeli vodoravno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Splits the current frame (which may be the main editing area) in two equally "
"sized frames, the new one below the current one. The new frame gets the "
"focus, and displays the same document as the old one."
msgstr ""
"Razdeli trenutni okvir (ki je lahko glavno območje urejanja) na dva okvirja "
"enake velikosti, novega pod trenutnim. Novi okvir dobi fokus in prikaže isti "
"dokument kot stari."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:889 menus.docbook:917 menus.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "See also <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Working with the &kate; MDI</link>"
msgstr "Glejte tudi <link linkend=\"kate-mdi\">Delo z &kate; MDI</link>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Document to New Vertical Split</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni dokument v novo navpično razdelitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the currently active view vertically into two views and move "
"the currently active document to right view."
msgstr ""
"To bo navpično razdelilo trenutno aktivni pogled na dva pogleda in "
"premaknilo trenutno aktivni dokument v desni pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Document to New Horizontal Split</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni dokument v novo vodoravno razdelitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will split the currently active view horizontally into two views and "
"move the currently active document to view below."
msgstr ""
"To bo vodoravno razdelilo trenutno aktivni pogled na dva pogleda in "
"premaknilo trenutno aktivni dokument na spodnji pogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Toggle Orientation</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preklop orientacije</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch between horizontal and vertical split."
msgstr "Preklopite med vodoravno in navpično delitvijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Close Current View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem >Zapri trenutni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes the active frame, which can be identified as the one displaying a "
"blinking cursor. This is disabled, if there is only one frame (the main "
"editing area)."
msgstr ""
"Zapre aktivni okvir, ki ga je mogoče identificirati kot tisti, ki prikazuje "
"utripajoč kazalec. To je onemogočeno, če obstaja samo en okvir (glavno "
"območje urejanja)."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:944 menus.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No documents get closed by closing a frame &ndash; they will still be "
"available in the <link linkend=\"view-menu\"><guimenu>View</guimenu> Menu</"
"link> as well as in the File List."
msgstr ""
"Noben dokument se ne zapre z zapiranjem okvirja &ndash; še vedno bodo na "
"voljo v <link linkend=\"view-menu\"><guimenu>meniju Pogled</guimenu></link> "
"kot tudi na seznamu datotek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Close Inactive Views</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zapri neaktivne poglede</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes all frames except the active frame (the one with a blinking cursor). "
"This is disabled, if there is only one frame (the main editing area)."
msgstr ""
"Zapre vse okvirje razen aktivnega (tistega z utripajočim kazalcem). To je "
"onemogočeno, če obstaja samo en okvir (glavno območje urejanja)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Hide "
"Inactive Views</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Deljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Skrij neaktivne poglede</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "This hides all split views except the currently active one."
msgstr "To skrije vse razdeljene poglede razen trenutno aktivnega."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Left</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni razdelilnik v levo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two vertically "
"split documents further left."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočen Razdeljeni pogled, bo to premaknilo mejo med dvema navpično "
"razdeljenima dokumentoma bolj levo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Right</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni razdelilnik desno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two vertically "
"split documents further right."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočen Razdeljeni pogled, bo to premaknilo mejo med dvema navpično "
"razdeljenima dokumentoma bolj desno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni razdelilnik navzgor</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two "
"horizontally split documents further up."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočen Razdeljeni pogled, bo to premaknilo mejo med dvema vodoravno "
"razdeljenima dokumentoma višje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Move "
"Splitter Down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Premakni razdelilnik navzdol</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Split View is enabled, this will move the border between two "
"horizontally split documents further down."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočen pogled Split, bo to premaknilo mejo med dvema vodoravno "
"razdeljenima dokumentoma nižje."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some common actions in the <guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</"
"guisubmenu> menu are available using the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-"
"left-right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> button at the top right corner of the editor window"
msgstr ""
"Nekatera običajna dejanja v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu> so na voljo z "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-"
"left-right-22 .png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> gumb v zgornjem desnem kotu okna urejevalnika"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap> </"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show Sidebars</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap> </"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži stranske vrstice</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the sidebar button rows. This command does not affect "
"the display of the sidebar content widgets, any sidebar that is visible will "
"stay visible, and if you assigned shortcuts to the commands below those will "
"of course continue to work."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz vrstic gumbov stranske vrstice. Ta ukaz ne vpliva na prikaz "
"gradnikov vsebine stranske vrstice, katera koli stranska vrstica, ki je "
"vidna, bo ostala vidna in če ste dodelili bližnjice spodnjim ukazom, bodo te "
"seveda še naprej delovale."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show <replaceable>Plugin</replaceable></guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pogledi orodij</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži <replaceable>Vtičnik</replaceable></guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A list of all enabled plugins. Use the checkbox in front of each item to "
"toggle the display of the tool view."
msgstr ""
"Seznam vseh omogočenih vtičnikov. S potrditvenim poljem pred vsakim "
"elementom preklopite prikaz pogleda orodja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycap>F7</keycap> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preklopi na ukazno vrstico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will toggle the display of the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"advanced-editing-tools-commandline.html\">built-in command line</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo preklopil prikaz <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-"
"tools-commandline.html\">vgrajene ukazne vrstice</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enlarge Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Povečaj pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "This increases the display font size."
msgstr "To poveča velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrink Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skrči pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1108
#, no-c-format
msgid "This decreases the display font size."
msgstr "To zmanjša velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Schema</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Shema</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lists the available color schemes. You can change the schema for "
"the current view here, to change the default schema you need to use the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors\">Fonts "
"&amp; Colors</ulink> page of the config dialog."
msgstr ""
"V tem meniju so navedene razpoložljive barvne sheme. Tukaj lahko spremenite "
"shemo za trenutni pogled, če želite spremeniti privzeto shemo, morate "
"uporabiti <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#prefcolors"
"\">Pisave &amp; Barve</ulink> stran konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dynamic Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelom Besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dinamični Prelom Besed </guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles dynamic word wrap in the current view. Dynamic word wrap makes all "
"the text in a view visible without the need for horizontal scrolling by "
"rendering one actual line on more visual lines as needed."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi dinamični prelom besed v trenutnem pogledu. Dinamično prelivanje "
"besed omogoča, da je celotno besedilo v pogledu vidno brez potrebe po "
"vodoravnem pomikanju, tako da po potrebi upodablja eno dejansko vrstico v "
"več vizualnih vrsticah."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Dynamic Word Wrap Indicators</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelivanje besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Indikatorji dinamičnega prelivanja besed</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when and how the dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed. "
"This is only available if the <guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> option "
"is checked."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kdaj in kako naj bodo prikazani indikatorji dinamičnega preloma "
"besed. To je na voljo le, če je označena možnost <guilabel>Dinamični prelom "
"besed</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Word Wrap</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Static Word Wrap Marker</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prelivanje besed</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži oznako statičnega prelivanja besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of a vertical line indicating the position of the wrap "
"width as configured in the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor."
"html#pref-wrap-words-at\">config dialog</ulink>. This feature requires that "
"you use a true fixed-width font."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz navpične črte, ki označuje položaj širine preloma, kot je "
"konfiguriran v <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-dialog-editor.html#pref-"
"wrap-words-at\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</ulink >. Ta funkcija "
"zahteva uporabo prave pisave s fiksno širino."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži obrobo ikone</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle item. Setting it on checked will make the Icon Border "
"visible in the left side of the active editor, and vice versa. The Icon "
"Border indicates the positions of the marked lines in the editor."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če je označeno, bo obroba ikone vidna na levi "
"strani aktivnega urejevalnika in obratno. Obroba ikone označuje položaje "
"označenih vrstic v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži številke vrstic</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle Item. Setting it on checked will make a pane displaying the "
"line numbers of the document visible in the left border of the active "
"editor, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če ga nastavite na označeno, bo podokno, ki "
"prikazuje številke vrstic dokumenta, vidno na levem robu aktivnega "
"urejevalnika in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Marks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži "
"oznake drsnega traku</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the visualization of bookmarks (and other marks) on the vertical "
"scrollbar. When enabled, a mark is represented by a thin line in the mark "
"color at the scrollbar, clicking the &MMB; on the line will scroll the view "
"to a position near the mark."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi vizualizacijo zaznamkov (in drugih oznak) na navpičnem drsnem "
"traku. Ko je omogočeno, je oznaka predstavljena s tanko črto v barvi oznake "
"na drsnem traku, s klikom gumba &MMB; na vrstici bo pomaknil pogled do "
"položaja blizu oznake."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Borders</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Scrollbar Mini-Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Meje</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"mini zemljevid z drsnim trakom</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will replace the scrollbar with a visualization of the current "
"document. For more information on the scrollbar minimap, see the <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/kate-part-scrollbar-minimap.html\">Scrollbar Minimap "
"section of the &katepart; Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To bo zamenjalo drsni trak z vizualizacijo trenutnega dokumenta. Za več "
"informacij o mini zemljevidu drsnega traku glejte razdelek <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/kate-part-scrollbar-minimap.html\">Mini zemljevid drsnega "
"traku v &katepart; Priročnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Code Folding</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zgibanje kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options pertain to <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">code folding</ulink>:"
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti se nanašajo na <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-"
"tools-code-folding.html\">zlaganje kode</ulink>:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zgibne oznake</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the folding marker pane in the left side of the view."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz zložljivega podokna označevalcev na levi strani pogleda."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fold Current Node"
msgstr "Zloži trenutno vozlišče"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Strni območje, ki vsebuje kazalec."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unfold Current Node"
msgstr "Razgrni trenutno vozlišče"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Razširite območje, ki vsebuje kazalec."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Fold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zloži vozlišča najvišje ravni</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collapse all toplevel regions in the document. Click on the right pointing "
"triangle to expand all toplevel regions."
msgstr ""
"Strni vse regije najvišje ravni v dokumentu. Kliknite desni trikotnik, da "
"razširite vse regije najvišje ravni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Unfold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Razgrni vozlišča najvišje ravni</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand all toplevel regions in the document."
msgstr "Razširite vse regije najvišje ravni v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Non-Printable Spaces"
msgstr "Pokaži nenatisljive prostore"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/hide bounding box around non-printable spaces."
msgstr "Pokaži/skrij omejevalni okvir okoli nenatisljivih presledkov."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the entries described here, one entry for each bookmark in the active "
"document will be available. The text will be the first few words of the "
"marked line. Choose an item to move the cursor to the start of that line. "
"The editor will scroll as necessary to make that line visible."
msgstr ""
"Pod tukaj opisanimi vnosi bo na voljo en vnos za vsak zaznamek v aktivnem "
"dokumentu. Besedilo bo prvih nekaj besed označene vrstice. Izberite element, "
"da premaknete kazalec na začetek te vrstice. Urejevalnik se bo po potrebi "
"pomaknil, da bo ta vrstica vidna."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavi zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets or removes a bookmark in the current line of the active document. (If "
"it's there, it is removed, otherwise one is set.)"
msgstr ""
"Sets or removes a bookmark in the current line of the active document. (If "
"it's there, it is removed, otherwise one is set.)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear All Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti vse zaznamke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will remove all the markers from the document as well as the "
"list of markers which is appended at the bottom of this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo odstranil vse oznake iz dokumenta, kot tudi seznam oznak, ki je "
"pripet na dnu tega menijskega elementa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the first above line with a "
"bookmark. The menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece "
"of text on the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in "
"a line above the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalec premakne na začetek prve zgornje vrstice z zaznamkom. "
"Besedilo menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del "
"besedila v vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici nad kazalcem "
"zaznamek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the next line with a bookmark. The "
"menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece of text on "
"the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in a line "
"below the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalec premakne na začetek naslednje vrstice z zaznamkom. Besedilo "
"menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del besedila v "
"vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici pod kazalcem zaznamek."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1363
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Sessions Menu"
msgstr "Meni Seje"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu contains entries for using and managing &kate; sessions. For more "
"information, read <link linkend=\"fundamentals-using-sessions\">Using "
"Sessions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vsebuje vnose za uporabo in upravljanje &kate; sej. Za več "
"informacij preberite <link linkend=\"fundamentals-using-sessions\">Uporaba "
"sej</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a new empty session. All currently open files will be closed."
msgstr "Ustvari novo prazno sejo. Vse trenutno odprte datoteke bodo zaprte."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Session...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odprta seja ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open an existing session. The Session Chooser dialog is displayed to let you "
"choose one."
msgstr ""
"Odprite obstoječo sejo. Prikaže se pogovorno okno Izbirnik seje, v katerem "
"lahko izberete enega."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Quick Open Session</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Hitra odprta seja</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1395
#, no-c-format
msgid "This submenu lets you open an existing session."
msgstr "Ta podmeni vam omogoča odpiranje obstoječe seje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Session</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani sejo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the current session. If the session is anonymous, you will be prompted "
"for a session name."
msgstr ""
"Shranite trenutno sejo. Če je seja anonimna, boste pozvani k vnosu imena "
"seje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Session As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani sejo kot ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the current session under a new name. You are prompted for a name to "
"use."
msgstr ""
"Shranite trenutno sejo pod novim imenom. Pozvani boste za ime, ki ga želite "
"uporabiti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Sessions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Sessions...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Seje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje sej ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the Session Manager dialog which allows you to rename and delete "
"sessions."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno upravitelja sej, ki vam omogoča preimenovanje in "
"brisanje sej."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Read Only Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način samo za branje</"
"guimenuitem><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način samo za branje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current document to Read Only mode. This prevents any text addition "
"and any changes in the document formatting."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite trenutni dokument v način samo za branje. To prepreči kakršno koli "
"dodajanje besedila in kakršne koli spremembe v oblikovanju dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Način</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the filetype scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/pref-open-save-modes-"
"filetypes.html\">filetype</ulink> mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in the Filetypes tab for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo vrste datoteke, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To "
"prepiše globalni način <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/pref-open-save-modes-"
"filetypes.html\">TipDatoteke</ulink>, nastavljen v <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kate;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> na zavihku Vrste datotek samo za vaš trenutni "
"dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Označevanje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the Highlighting scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global highlighting mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo označevanja, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način označevanja, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Indentation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zamik</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-autoindent.html\">style of "
"indentation</ulink> you want for your active document. This overwrites the "
"global indentation mode set in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> for "
"your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-autoindent.html\">slog "
"zamika</ulink>, ki ga želite za svoj aktivni dokument. To prepiše globalni "
"način zamika, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kodiranje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can overwrite the default encoding set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Open/Save</guilabel> page to set a different "
"encoding for your current document. The encoding you set here will be only "
"valid for your current document."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto kodiranje lahko prepišete v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> na strani <guilabel>Odpri/Shrani</guilabel>, da nastavite "
"drugačno kodiranje za vaš trenutni dokument. Kodiranje, ki ga nastavite "
"tukaj, bo veljavno samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>End of Line</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Konec vrstice</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global end of line mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite želeni način konca vrstice za vaš aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način konca vrstice, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Add Byte Mark Order (BOM)</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dodaj vrstni red oznak bajtov (BOM)</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this action you can explicitly add a byte order mark for unicode "
"encoded documents. The byte order mark (BOM) is a Unicode character used to "
"signal the endianness (byte order) of a text file or stream, for more "
"information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark"
"\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to dejanje, lahko izrecno dodate oznako vrstnega reda bajtov za "
"dokumente, kodirane z Unicode. Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov (BOM) je znak "
"Unicode, ki se uporablja za signalizacijo endianness (vrstni red bajtov) "
"besedilne datoteke ali toka, za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\" >Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Scripts</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skripte</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu contains a list of all scripted actions. The list can easily be "
"modified by <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-scripting-"
"command-line\">writing your own scripts</ulink>. This way, &kate; can be "
"extended with user-defined tools."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni vsebuje seznam vseh skriptiranih dejanj. Seznam lahko preprosto "
"spremenite tako, da <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-"
"scripting-command-line\">napišete lastne skripte</ulink>. Na ta način &kate; "
"se lahko razširi z uporabniško določenimi orodji."

#. Tag: ulink
#: menus.docbook:1541
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is a complete list of scripts in the &katepart; documentation."
msgstr "Celoten seznam skriptov je v &katepart; dokumentacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invoke Code Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikliči dokončanje kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manually invoke command completion, usually by using a shortcut bound to "
"this action."
msgstr ""
"Ročno prikličite dokončanje ukaza, običajno z uporabo bližnjice, vezane na "
"to dejanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Word Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dokončanje besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Reuse Word Below</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) and <guimenuitem>Reuse Word Above</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo>) complete the currently typed text by searching for similar words "
"backward or forward from the current cursor position. <guimenuitem>Shell "
"Completion</guimenuitem> pops up a completion box with matching entries."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Znova uporabi besedo spodaj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) in <guimenuitem>Ponovno "
"uporabi besedo zgoraj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>) dokončajte trenutno vtipkano besedilo z "
"iskanjem podobnih besed nazaj ali naprej od trenutnega položaja kazalca. "
"<guimenuitem>Dokončanje lupine</guimenuitem> odpre polje za dokončanje z "
"ujemajočimi se vnosi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem> is enabled, wrongly "
"spelled text is underlined in the document on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno <guimenuitem>Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>, "
"je napačno črkovano besedilo v dokumentu sproti podčrtano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Črkovanje ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:1595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to help the "
"user catch and correct any spelling errors."
msgstr ""
"To sproži program za preverjanje črkovanja - program, ki je zasnovan tako, "
"da uporabniku pomaga odkriti in popraviti morebitne črkovalne napake."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on how to use the &kde; spellchecking program, see the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/spellcheck.html\"><emphasis>Check Spelling</"
"emphasis> section of the <emphasis>&kde; Fundamentals</emphasis> "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o uporabi &kde; program za preverjanje črkovanja, glejte "
"razdelek <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/spellcheck.html"
"\"><emphasis>Preverjanje črkovanja</emphasis> v <emphasis>&kde; Osnove</"
"emphasis> dokumentacija</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Črkovanje (iz kazalke)...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program but it starts where your cursor is "
"instead of at the beginning of the document."
msgstr ""
"To zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja, vendar se začne tam, kjer je vaš "
"kazalka, namesto na začetku dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izbira preverjanja črkovanja ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecks the current selection."
msgstr "Preveri črkovanje trenutnega izbora."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Spelling</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spremeni slovar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a drop down box with all available dictionaries for spellchecking "
"at the bottom of the editor window. This allows easy switching of the "
"spellcheck dictionary &eg; for automatic spellcheck of text in different "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže spustno polje z vsemi razpoložljivimi slovarji za preverjanje "
"črkovanja na dnu okna urejevalnika. To omogoča preprosto preklapljanje med "
"slovarjem za preverjanje črkovanja &eg; za samodejno preverjanje črkovanja "
"besedila v različnih jezikih."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections about the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</"
"ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals with these additional entries:"
msgstr ""
"&kate; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z nastavitvami</"
"ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">meni "
"Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove s temi dodatnimi vnosi:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Color Theme</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Barvna tema</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use a different color scheme from the system’s global color schemes "
"described in the &systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors/"
"index.html\">Colors</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite drugačno barvno shemo od sistemskih globalnih barvnih shem, "
"opisanih v &systemsettings; modul <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/colors/index."
"html\">Barve</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Tabs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zavihke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tabs are moveable using the &LMB; and have actions in the context menu to "
"close documents, copy the path to the clipboard or open the folder of the "
"document in the filemanager. Using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"view-"
"quick-open\"><guibutton>Quick Open</guibutton> </link> button makes "
"switching between documents easy. Click the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-left-"
"right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"with the &LMB; to open a menu with actions from the <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Split View</guisubmenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Zavihke lahko premikate z &LMB; in imate dejanja v kontekstnem meniju za "
"zapiranje dokumentov, kopiranje poti do odložišča ali odpiranje mape "
"dokumenta v upravitelju datotek. Uporaba "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"quickopen-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <link linkend=\"view-"
"quick-open\"><guibutton>Quick Gumb Odpri</guibutton> </link> olajša "
"preklapljanje med dokumenti. Kliknite gumb "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-split-left-"
"right-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> z &LMB; da "
"odprete meni z dejanji iz menija <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Razdeljeni pogled</guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Path in Titlebar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži pot v naslovni vrstici</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled the full path of the active document is displayed, otherwise only "
"the filename. This is useful if you edit several files with the same "
"filename to distinguish them."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, je prikazana celotna pot aktivnega dokumenta, sicer pa samo "
"ime datoteke. To je uporabno, če urejate več datotek z istim imenom, da jih "
"ločite."
